---
title: Pork Satay Burgers with Paprika Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Satay is usually done with chicken, but we’ve gone a bit ‘out there’ and created our very own pork satay burger! When you add in the zinginess of the lime and the creamy crunch of peanuts - you’ve got yourself a
burger that is beyond scrumptious!
